Author: damien
Title: Introspective Robot Learns to Walk
Content:
Video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ehno85yI-sA

"Towards the end of the video, the robot conceptualizes itself, determining its own structure using sensors built into each joint. Then, it thinks of different ways that it might move - walk - from place to place. Starfish can also sense damage to any of its legs or joints, and then compensate."

Author: gtopala
Title: SIW - Everything you want to know about your PC
Content: SIW is a tool that gathers detailed information about your system properties and settings. A utility that includes detailed specs for Hardware, Software and Network. Product Key (CD key), Serial Numbers, Password Recovery, behind asterisks Passwords..
